@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f0f1b;
            color: #fafbf6;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #c6b7be;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        strong {
            color: #c6b7be;
        }

        .highlight {
            background-color: #c6b7be;
            color: #0f0f1b;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to our Project</h1>
        <p>
            Our project is an innovative web application built with ASP.NET Core that aims to revolutionize how users
            interact with temperature data. Leveraging the power of modern web technologies, we provide a seamless and
            intuitive experience for visualizing and analyzing temperature data in real-time.
        </p>

        <p>
            With our application, users can easily access temperature data from various sensors and devices. We provide
            rich visualization tools, including interactive charts and graphs, to help users understand trends and
            patterns in the data. Whether you're a researcher, scientist, or enthusiast, our platform offers valuable
            insights into temperature fluctuations and their impact on the environment.
        </p>

        <p>
            One of the key features of our project is its integration with external APIs and services. We retrieve
            temperature data from external sources, process it in real-time, and present it to users in a clear and
            meaningful way. Our platform also supports data export and sharing, allowing users to collaborate and
            exchange insights with others.
        </p>

        <p>
            Security is a top priority for us. We implement robust authentication and authorization mechanisms to
            protect user data and ensure privacy. Our application follows industry best practices for secure development
            and undergoes regular security audits and assessments.
        </p>

        <p>
            In summary, our project offers a cutting-edge solution for exploring and analyzing temperature data. Whether
            you're a professional researcher or a curious hobbyist, our platform provides the tools and insights you
            need to make informed decisions and drive meaningful change.
        </p>

        <p>
            Ready to get started? <strong>Sign up</strong> today and join the temperature data revolution!
        </p>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p>Sign up now and unlock exclusive features!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
